==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Bungu'''

# {{geography}} A city in [[Tanzania]].
# {{linguistics}} An African language of the [[Niger-Congo]] language family.
# Vuyani '''Bungu''', a featherweight African boxer.

===Common noun===
# {{botany}} A plant, ''Ceratotheca sesamoides'', placed among the ''Pedaliaceae'' (pedalium family or sesame family).

